org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 582, \"end\": 588, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Denali\", \"score\": 0.99997658511362, \"rank\": 2.341534918860019e-05, \"text\": \"Denali\", \"types\": [\"Q8502\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Denali\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Denali\"}, {\"begin\": 592, \"end\": 598, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alaska\", \"score\": 0.9999999999956799, \"rank\": 4.345505770944497e-12, \"text\": \"Alaska\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alaska\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alaska\"}, {\"begin\": 602, \"end\": 608, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Acadia_National_Park\", \"score\": 0.9888358048512017, \"rank\": 0.01124712757165326, \"text\": \"Acadia\", \"types\": [\"Q473972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Acadia_National_Park\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Acadia_National_Park\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"nine parks\", \"from\": 540, \"to\": 550}, {\"ngram\": \"Maine\", \"from\": 612, \"to\": 617}, {\"ngram\": \"our parks\", \"from\": 647, \"to\": 656}, {\"ngram\": \"climate change\", \"from\": 676, \"to\": 690}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Few trips have been more eye opening than this tour of Olympic National Park,\\\" Quigley said.\", \"from\": 692, \"to\": 784, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 771, \"end\": 778, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Allie_Quigley\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.680599387471042e-18, \"text\": \"Quigley\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Allie_Quigley\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Allie_Quigley\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Few trips\", \"from\": 692, \"to\": 701}, {\"ngram\": \"more eye opening\", \"from\": 712, \"to\": 728}, {\"ngram\": \"this tour\", \"from\": 734, \"to\": 743}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic National Park\", \"from\": 747, \"to\": 768}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Olympic is home to some of our nation's most captivating glaciers and as a result of rapidly warming temperatures, they are disappearing right before our eyes.\", \"from\": 785, \"to\": 945, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Olympic\", \"from\": 786, \"to\": 793}, {\"ngram\": \"our nation's most captivating glaciers\", \"from\": 813, \"to\": 851}, {\"ngram\": \"a result\", \"from\": 859, \"to\": 867}, {\"ngram\": \"rapidly warming temperatures\", \"from\": 871, \"to\": 899}, {\"ngram\": \"our eyes\", \"from\": 936, \"to\": 944}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As they melt, the ecosystems within them struggle to survive, causing ripple effects across the country.\", \"from\": 946, \"to\": 1050, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the ecosystems\", \"from\": 960, \"to\": 974}, {\"ngram\": \"ripple effects\", \"from\": 1016, \"to\": 1030}, {\"ngram\": \"the country\", \"from\": 1038, \"to\": 1049}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We also witnessed how warming temperatures and rising sea levels are influencing not only marine life, but the native tribes that have called the Olympic Peninsula home for hundreds of years.\", \"from\": 1051, \"to\": 1242, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"warming temperatures\", \"from\": 1073, \"to\": 1093}, {\"ngram\": \"rising sea levels\", \"from\": 1098, \"to\": 1115}, {\"ngram\": \"not only marine life\", \"from\": 1132, \"to\": 1152}, {\"ngram\": \"the native tribes\", \"from\": 1158, \"to\": 1175}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Peninsula\", \"from\": 1193, \"to\": 1214}, {\"ngram\": \"hundreds\", \"from\": 1224, \"to\": 1232}, {\"ngram\": \"years\", \"from\": 1236, \"to\": 1241}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Congress must continue to address climate change and help ensure Olympic and all of our National Parks continue to thrive amidst this pressing threat.\", \"from\": 1243, \"to\": 1393, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1243, \"end\": 1251, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Congress\", \"score\": 0.9993919931811487, \"rank\": 0.0006083766478924274, \"text\": \"Congress\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q11204\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Congress\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Congress\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"climate change\", \"from\": 1277, \"to\": 1291}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic\", \"from\": 1308, \"to\": 1315}, {\"ngram\": \"our National Parks\", \"from\": 1327, \"to\": 1345}, {\"ngram\": \"this pressing threat\", \"from\": 1372, \"to\": 1392}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If we do not act, generations of Americans after us will be left wondering why we failed them and why we failed to protect our national treasures from climate change.\\\"\", \"from\": 1394, \"to\": 1561, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"generations\", \"from\": 1412, \"to\": 1423}, {\"ngram\": \"Americans\", \"from\": 1427, \"to\": 1436}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 1443, \"to\": 1445}, {\"ngram\": \"our national treasures\", \"from\": 1517, \"to\": 1539}, {\"ngram\": \"climate change\", \"from\": 1545, \"to\": 1559}]}, {\"sentence\": \"According to Kilmer, whose district encompasses Olympic National Park, a critical part of his job is to elevate the issues important to his constituents' region.\", \"from\": 1563, \"to\": 1724, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Kilmer\", \"from\": 1576, \"to\": 1582}, {\"ngram\": \"whose district\", \"from\": 1584, \"to\": 1598}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic National Park\", \"from\": 1611, \"to\": 1632}, {\"ngram\": \"a critical part\", \"from\": 1634, \"to\": 1649}, {\"ngram\": \"his job\", \"from\": 1653, \"to\": 1660}, {\"ngram\": \"the issues\", \"from\": 1675, \"to\": 1685}, {\"ngram\": \"his constituents' region\", \"from\": 1699, \"to\": 1723}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Our region is seeing firsthand how climate change is impacting public lands and putting local economies at risk.\", \"from\": 1726, \"to\": 1839, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Our region\", \"from\": 1727, \"to\": 1737}, {\"ngram\": \"climate change\", \"from\": 1762, \"to\": 1776}, {\"ngram\": \"public lands\", \"from\": 1790, \"to\": 1802}, {\"ngram\": \"local economies\", \"from\": 1815, \"to\": 1830}, {\"ngram\": \"risk\", \"from\": 1834, \"to\": 1838}]}, {\"sentence\": \"From highlighting tribal communities moving to higher ground because of rising sea levels, to the work being done to protect theenvironmentalhealth of Olympic National Park, it was valuable to showcase the impacts of climate change on our region to Members of Congress who focus on these issues and serve on key committees back in DC.\", \"from\": 1840, \"to\": 2174, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2100, \"end\": 2108, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Congress\", \"score\": 0.9993919931811487, \"rank\": 0.0006083766478924274, \"text\": \"Congress\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q11204\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Congress\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Congress\"}, {\"begin\": 2171, \"end\": 2174, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Augustin_Pyramus_de_Candolle\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"DC.\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Augustin_Pyramus_de_Candolle\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Augustin_Pyramus_de_Candolle\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"tribal communities\", \"from\": 1858, \"to\": 1876}, {\"ngram\": \"higher ground\", \"from\": 1887, \"to\": 1900}, {\"ngram\": \"rising sea levels\", \"from\": 1912, \"to\": 1929}, {\"ngram\": \"the work\", \"from\": 1934, \"to\": 1942}, {\"ngram\": \"theenvironmentalhealth\", \"from\": 1965, \"to\": 1987}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic National Park\", \"from\": 1991, \"to\": 2012}, {\"ngram\": \"the impacts\", \"from\": 2042, \"to\": 2053}, {\"ngram\": \"climate change\", \"from\": 2057, \"to\": 2071}, {\"ngram\": \"our region\", \"from\": 2075, \"to\": 2085}, {\"ngram\": \"Members\", \"from\": 2089, \"to\": 2096}, {\"ngram\": \"these issues\", \"from\": 2122, \"to\": 2134}, {\"ngram\": \"key committees\", \"from\": 2148, \"to\": 2162}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am grateful to my colleagues who took the time to visit our neck of the woods and hear from local community leaders, park officials, tribes, and environmental advocates,\\\" Kilmer said.\", \"from\": 2175, \"to\": 2360, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my colleagues\", \"from\": 2192, \"to\": 2205}, {\"ngram\": \"the time\", \"from\": 2215, \"to\": 2223}, {\"ngram\": \"our neck\", \"from\": 2233, \"to\": 2241}, {\"ngram\": \"the woods\", \"from\": 2245, \"to\": 2254}, {\"ngram\": \"local community leaders\", \"from\": 2269, \"to\": 2292}, {\"ngram\": \"park officials\", \"from\": 2294, \"to\": 2308}, {\"ngram\": \"tribes\", \"from\": 2310, \"to\": 2316}, {\"ngram\": \"environmental advocates\", \"from\": 2322, \"to\": 2345}, {\"ngram\": \"Kilmer\", \"from\": 2348, \"to\": 2354}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The SEEC is a coalition of 98 members of the U.S. House of Representatives founded in January 2009 to be a focused, active and effective coalition for advancing policies that address climate change, promote clean energy innovation and domestic manufacturing, develop renewable energy resources, create family-sustaining clean jobs, protect our nation's air, water, and natural environment and promote environmental justice.\", \"from\": 2362, \"to\": 2785, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The SEEC\", \"from\": 2362, \"to\": 2370}, {\"ngram\": \"a coalition\", \"from\": 2374, \"to\": 2385}, {\"ngram\": \"98 members\", \"from\": 2389, \"to\": 2399}, {\"ngram\": \"the U.S. House\", \"from\": 2403, \"to\": 2417}, {\"ngram\": \"Representatives\", \"from\": 2421, \"to\": 2436}, {\"ngram\": \"January\", \"from\": 2448, \"to\": 2455}, {\"ngram\": \"a